### TABLE API ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### Get All Tables
GET {{baseUrl}}/tables

### Get All Tables Filtered by Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/tables?status=free

### Get All Tables Filtered by Location
GET {{baseUrl}}/tables?area=674da30bb19ecab3d0c9f0c2

